This is the website to get free icons to be used in your website

copy this script into the html file before the title

<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/9451b2b3fc.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>


then now you can look for the icons you need and copy the code

eg...
<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/9451b2b3fc.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>



<body>
    <i class="fa-solid fa-house fa-fade"></i> #icon of a house

</body>